{"id":839581,"date":[{"year":1991,"month":5,"day":22}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"生活","special_issue":"生活","column":"爱的珠玑","genre":"","count":"94","ytitle":"","mtitle":"爱就是……","ftitle":"","authors":["陈刚"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱就是逃避，逃避中的频频回首；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱就是不安，不安里的点点蜜意；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱就是无端，无端想起你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱就是反复，反复为你吟唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱就是恨，恨中的不舍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱就是恨，恨意绵绵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——陈刚"}]}